cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new representation for recurrent fuzzy systems and uses evolutionary algorithms to automate the development process of fuzzy controllers. This work is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for the development of intelligent controllers, robotics (cs.RO) for the application of the proposed method in evolutionary robotics, machine learning (cs.LG) for the use of evolutionary algorithms, control systems (cs.SY) for the development of controllers, and neural networks (cs.NE) for the use of internal units as memory elements.
